In this example: 

```son
curl -XGET localhost:9200/tweets/_search -d '{
  "query" : {
    "filtered" : {
        "filter" : {
            "terms" : {
                "user" : {
                    "index" : "users",
                    "type" : "user",
                    "id" : "2",
                    "path" : "friends"
                }
            }
        }
    }
  }
}
```

Say I wanted to pass an array of ids instead of a single id as it's shown `"id" : "2"` 

Reason is I have several documents I want to combine.
